Simple Automated Scripts to build OpenWRT for Qemu on a x86 platform.

	1. /scripts/fetch.sh
		-Fetches required source files from openwrt.org

	2. /scripts/configure.sh
		-Confgures OpenWRT kernel for Qemu on a x86 platform

	3. /scripts/build.sh
		-Builds OpenWRT with customized kernel for x86
	
	4. /scripts/build-modules.sh
		- Builds modules outside OpenWRT Installation

	5. /scripts/launch.sh
		-Launches OpenWRT on Qemu

